  "commentary": "With SPX at 7009.52 trading just above the massive 7000 gamma wall (19.26B), dealers are likely selling into this strength as they're long gamma in PIN regime. The thick positive gamma concentration between 7000-7025 creates a strong magnetic pull that should cap upside momentum and encourage mean reversion back toward these strikes. Watch 7000 as the critical pivot - breaks below likely accelerate selling toward the 6860 flip level, while sustained moves above 7025 would need to overcome another 14.4B gamma wall.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pulled back toward the 7000-7025 zone with limited upside momentum.",
